{"word":"Δωρίς","slug":"Δωρίς","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>Δωρίς</b></el> <p/><a href='S:feminine'>fem.</a> <a href='S:Adjective'>adj.</a> <i>Dorian</i>, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>: hence,<p/><div class='li750'><b>1. </b><el>Δωρὶς νᾶσος</el> <i>the Dorian island</i>, <a href='S:id est'>i. e.</a> <i>Peloponnesus</i>, <b><a href='S:Pindar'>Pind.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>2. </b>(with or without <el>γῆ</el>) <i>Doris</i>, in Northern Greece, <b><a href='S:Herodotus'>Hdt.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Thucydides'>Thuc.</a></b>, <a href='S:et cetera'>etc.</a><p/></div><div class='li750'><b>3. </b><el>Δ. κόρα</el> <i>a Dorian damsel</i>, <b><a href='S:Euripides'>Eur.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}